text:
Thank you very much for today.
It was fun!

Yes, thanks for your hard work!
I'm looking forward to working with you again!

Let's see...
It's the day after tomorrow, isn't it!

I'll double check my schedule,
but would it be alright if I came to watch it?
Oh course, that's fine with us!

Fufuu, thank you!
I'll confirm that I can then!

("Done with teh recording,
Heading to the photo shoot now")
Can you shift your gaze over this way a bit?

Good, thanks. This is good, Hana-chan.
This'll make a great picture!

...I can't really say for sure myself,
but I think it's good.

Got it. ...Well, since the subject of the
picture is already good... right?

I'm glad I was able to get some great pictures today.
Thank you.
You're full of compliments, aren't you──
